LOCUS       pHAGE2_EF1A_PB1_       10962 bp    DNA     circular SYN 17-DEC-2025
DEFINITION  Made by Sheri Harari in Decemnber of 2024. This construct was made 
            for creation of TMPRSS2 stable cells. Construct is similar to 2850 
            but with gene of interest rin B2) followed by T2A linker and 
            mCherry. Also includes PuroR after CMV oter. Puro resistant marker 
            was changed to Hygro resistance. This will allow for Hygro selection
            as well as Puro selection in case of cells that already contain puro
            resistance.
            All the fragments of this plasmids were PCR aplified and assembled 
            together using gibson assembly. Sequence confirmed with Primordium. 
            This plasmid contain kozak sequence before the TMPRSS2 to allow 
            medium levels of expressions in the resulting clones.
ACCESSION   TMPRSS2_MED_1
